data.description: Beautifully updated and remodeled home in Morris Heights Subdivision. Granite kitchen counters, newer kitchen cabinets, huge pantry, open floorplan, newer Furnace and Central AC! Fantastic backyard with lots of room and tons of privacy. Minutes to Highways, CU Medical Center, VA Hospital, Shopping, Entertainment.... Move-in ready, feels like a new build, brick exterior. Basement has non-conforming bedroom, lots of space for workout room in basement, washer/dryer hook-ups. Must see, fantastic home, you will not be disappointed!!
